Changes
=======

9th June 2022

BASIC: 	Fixed WHILE bug reported by Tsvetan.
		Tokeniser now does REM for you (e.g. REM a comment will tokenise as REM "a comment")
		CLEAR can take a parameter setting the highest memory value.
		BASIC Code address dropped to $3400 and edtest made to work by pushing test code 4k up.
		Implemented READ, RESTORE and DATA

20th June 2022

BASIC: 	Added GOTO, GOSUB and RETURN for old code. Will not work with editor.		
		Variables cleared/Stack reset etc. after directly editing code.